cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI. 

The paper is about distributed learning with attack or error, which is a subfield of machine learning. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the application of distributed learning in edge computing and federated learning, which falls under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also deals with security issues, such as malicious attacks, which is a subfield of computer security, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper proposes a new method for distributed learning, which involves optimization algorithms, and hence, it can be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper uses empirical results to evaluate the proposed method, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
